Dear [Name],

I am writing to inform you that I am feeling unwell and will need to take a sick leave. I am experiencing [symptoms] and have visited a doctor, who has advised me to take a few days off to rest and recover.

I understand that this may be inconvenient, but I am confident that I will be able to return to work soon. I will keep you updated on my progress and will be available if you need any additional information.

Thank you for your understanding.

Sincerely,
[Your Name]